@raghav_chadha Companies should move some operations out of metros like Mumbai, Pune, Delhi, Bengaluru.

Cities like Jaipur, Indore, Ahmedabad, Surat, Lucknow, Nagpur have huge potential.

Less traffic, less migration, lower costs better for everyone.

